scopes.name: schedule_only
scopes.explanation: The ISDA Schedule begins at line 358 ("SCHEDULE to the ISDA 2002 Master Agreement...") and continues through the signature block at line 461. This section contains the negotiated terms between the parties, including elections, representations, and other provisions specific to the parties, which is the content of the Schedule. The preceding lines are the standard pre-printed Master Agreement, and the following lines are signatures. No CSA annexes are present in this excerpt.
